{"article_id":"Fh7NNw8Cei0GLabt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The battleground state of Florida just became even more unpredictable","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"now that felons in the state have regained the right","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"to vote .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Amendment 4 , a ballot initiative","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that was approved by nearly two-thirds of Floridians ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"granted approximately 1.4 million convicted felons","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"who have completed their sentences","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"the right","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to vote on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"The measure excludes those convicted of murder and sex crimes .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"The move expands the pool of eligible voters in Florida by roughly 1.4 million people","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"- a significant number in a state","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"where elections are often decided by fewer than 100,000 votes -","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"setting off a scramble","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to register eligible felons . [ ... ]","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Exactly which party stands to benefit the most from the new pool of eligible voters remains uncertain ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"according to multiple experts and activists .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"It ' s also unclear just how many felons will actually register","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"to vote .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Democratic candidates in the 2018 midterm elections overwhelmingly endorsed Amendment 4 ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"even making it a key part of their campaigns .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"including Sen. Rick Scott ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"largely opposed it .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"( The Hill )","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"\" When you have a number of potential voters as large as that ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the potential for change in Florida is theoretically enormous , \"","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Mac Stipanovich , a Republican strategist , told The Hill .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"\" We ' re a state","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"where statewide elections ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"where millions of votes are cast ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"are decided by a few thousand votes . \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Indeed , both former Democratic Sen. Bill Nelson narrowly lost his race against Rick Scott","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"and Tallahassee Mayor Andrew Gillum","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"( D )","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"fell short against former Rep. Ron DeSantis by less than 33,000 votes .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"How the restoration of those rights will be handled remains to be seen , however .","depth":3},{"id":37,"text":"Gov . DeSantis said earlier this week","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"that an implementing bill may be necessary by the Legislature","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"to make the process clear .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"\" There ' s going to need to be guidance for that .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"It ' s not delaying it .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"The people spoke on it .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"It ' s going to be implemented ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"but I think","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"it needs to be implemented the way","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"people intended ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that they wanted to see any sex offenders fall through the cracks , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":52,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":0,"right":51,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":51,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":84,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":67,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":